
  Vanillish    Ice Type Pokémon

  Snowy mountains are this Pokémon’s 
  habitat.  During an ancient ice 
  age, they moved to southern areas. 
  
	   Evolution Chain
  Vanillite ► Vanillish ► Vanilluxe

