 ↞---------------|ABILITIES|---------------↠

  Ice-body:

    This Pokémon heals for 1/16 
  of its maximum HP after each 
  turn during hail, and it does 
  not take hail damage regardless 
  of type.

  Snow-cloak:

    During hail, this Pokémon has 
  1.25× its evasion, and it does 
  not take hail damage regardless 
  of type.

  The evasion bonus does not 
  count as a stat modifier.

  Overworld: If the lead Pokémon 
  has this ability, the wild encounter 
  rate is halved in snow.

  Weak-armor:

    Whenever a physical move hits 
  this Pokémon, its Speed rises 
  one stage and its Defense falls 
  one stage.

  This ability triggers on every 
  hit of a multiple-hit move.


 Location Areas:
   Dragonspiral tower entrance
   Dragonspiral tower outside
   Giant chasm outside
   Giant chasm area
